snippet.title: Cyclone Walkthrough, ZX Spectrum
snippet.description:
A walkthrough of the ZX Spectrum game, Cyclone. From the recording originally sent to http://www.rzxarchive.co.uk/

There is no ending as such. After all 5 crates have been picked up, another 5 appear and the process starts again.

#ZXSpectrum #RetroGaming #Walkthrough
